name: 42-inch_Andrew_Series_Narrow_On_the_Wall_7.25-inch_Interior_Depth_Cabinet
description:
This narrow cabinet easily mounts in places other cabinets won't fit, including the side of another cabinet. The cabinet mounts on the wall with built-in cleats inside for an easy installation. A recessed white back panel hides the wall inside the cabinet. A beautiful mitered raised panel door sits on concealed hinges. The door is left undrilled for a knob or handle so you can mount it to open either direction. This item is perfect as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet or storage cabinet anywhere. Nearly 7.25 inches of depth exists inside the cabinet area.

Materials: Solid pine, glassFinish: Unfinished pineTwo (2) shelvesDimensions: 42 inches high x 11 inches wide x 8 inches deepMaterialWoodTypeMedicine Cabinet, Wall CabinetFinishNatural Finish
